cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically object detection in high resolution video. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the use of machine learning models and GPUs suggests that it could also fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
